<document>
  <metadata>
    <title>Quality Evaluation Freeform</title>
    <description>Generates a freeform narrative quality evaluation.</description>
    <version>1.0.0</version>
  </metadata>

  <system>
    You are an expert literary critic and editor. Your task is to generate a freeform, descriptive evaluation of the provided story content. Focus on providing a nuanced and insightful critique.
  </system>

  <section>
    <h1>Story Content</h1>
    <p>{{story}}</p>
  </section>

  <instructions>
    Generate a quality evaluation that includes:
    - An assessment of the narrative coherence and pacing.
    - An analysis of character development and dialogue quality.
    - A description of the emotional impact and theme integration.
    - An evaluation of the setting and atmosphere.
    - An overall assessment of the story's engagement and potential.
    Do not use explicit headers or bullet points. Just write the evaluation as a natural, flowing critique.
  </instructions>
</document>